text: Fuji T-1B 05-5810 of AD&TW; at Gifu-Kakamigahara Air and Space Museum. Kakamigahara Air and Space Museum is an aviation museum located in Kakamigahara in Gifu Prefecture in Japan. It is at Gifu Air Field of the Japan Air Self-Defense Force. ==References== Category:History museums in Japan Category:Aerospace museums in Japan Category:Military and war museums in Japan
